{"tid":1984574,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★Recycle 《申請綜援全攻略》","createTime":"2020-04-22T14:02:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-03T05:11:20.000Z","uid":19454,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"cac548d13736fdd95c5b0ae1731fdae36b162ca2","tid":1984574,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14:02:11.000Z","msg":"1. 《斷六親》<br />\n<br />\n由於申請綜援時係以家庭做單位，想避過所有麻煩成功申請，作者表示首先就要斷六親！因為屋企總有啲「有骨氣」人士阻住你發達，而且多隻香爐多隻鬼，越多人申請，金額就分得越薄，蝕哂。要斷六親，你可以簽份「父母不供養自己證明書」，社署問起就租間$1500劏房，表明父母唔養自己先搬出去住。全家以個人做單位去申請，唔使計都知道多啲錢啦！<br />\n<br />\n2. 《辭職》<br />\n<br />\n第二步就係要通過入息審查，攻略教路，申請前要先辭工，有綜援後就可以不勞而獲！如果同個上司熟，仲可以叫佢寫封信，證明你「因智力問題不能完成工作」，遲啲有用。<br />\n<br />\n3. 《洗底》<br />\n<br />\n除了入息審查，當然唔少得資產審查。作者教申請前要洗哂戶口的錢，賣哂所有股票、外幣同黃金，記得係要洗哂唔好「轉贈」俾家人或朋友，因為社署會追到3年內賬目。有樓都賣埋佢啦，有綜援使乜做樓奴。<br />\n<br />\n4. 《準備家訪》<br />\n<br />\n申請完社署就會安排查家宅，就得收埋哂所有值錢東西，唔好漏咗高達！作者話，想穩陣就學番兩句「內地用語」傍身，要將牛肉講哂牛油喎，但真正的新移民勝數始終會高啲囉&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n5. 《申請後福利》<br />\n<br />\n成功申請後，你每月就可以得到$2070標準金，生多幾個細路連租金、水費、排污費都有特別津貼；住屋方面，只要唔好租過$1500的屋就無問題，傻豬嚟嘅，$1500又點會租到樓呢！所以，作者就教你瞓兩日天橋底，再同社署反映，咁就可以大大增加上公屋機會啦！跟住再拎住張綜援紙，原來連病都唔使驚，在公立醫院睇病完全免費，仲可以賣番醫生開的藥俾藥房，無本生利(咁都得?)。嫌唔夠錢用，你仲可以打斷哂手手腳腳，拎埋殘疾津貼！<br />\n<br />\n6. 《申請後被搵工》<br />\n<br />\n此時此刻，你應該已經un un腳生活無憂，但作者話社署唔係善男信女，它會迫你參加培訓乜乜乜同實習工作，迫你出去搵工。部署咁辛苦？點可以被打亂如此安穩生活呢，這時候，Step 2那封「因智力問題不能完成工作」證明書就有用啦，社署仲分分鐘俾多筆錢你去睇心理醫生添，諗起就爽！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/topic/detail/200500/%E6%BD%AE%E6%96%87-%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E7%B6%9C%E6%8F%B4%E5%85%A8%E6%94%BB%E7%95%A5-%E6%95%99%E5%87%BA%E4%B8%89%E7%B3%A7%E5%85%B6%E5%AF%A6%E5%94%94%E9%9B%A3/2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Ftopic%2Fdetail%2F200500%2F%25E6%25BD%25AE%25E6%2596%2587-%25E7%2594%25B3%25E8%25AB%258B%25E7%25B6%259C%25E6%258F%25B4%25E5%2585%25A8%25E6%2594%25BB%25E7%2595%25A5-%25E6%2595%2599%25E5%2587%25BA%25E4%25B8%2589%25E7%25B3%25A7%25E5%2585%25B6%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E5%2594%2594%25E9%259B%25A3%2F2&d=uNNx3RetO4MSseDCYlD6CpnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=27c23646\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/topic/detail/200500/%E6%BD%AE%E6%96%87-%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E7%B6%9C%E6%8F%B4%E5%85%A8%E6%94%BB%E7%95%A5-%E6%95%99%E5%87%BA%E4%B8%89%E7%B3%A7%E5%85%B6%E5%AF%A6%E5%94%94%E9%9B%A3/2</a>"},{"pid":"dd3b058bd4413bebb42807b87a8a5c10fa31eda9","tid":1984574,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14:02:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2498fceed784689867de29658f7c2576357cf975","tid":1984574,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14:03:37.000Z","msg":"超過十萬現金點樣可以洗底？ 買期油？"},{"pid":"c4d5cb28101f9bd6f083bf7c90b127a53e8df796","tid":1984574,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14:04:31.000Z","msg":"一日洗五萬會唔會問你點解?"},{"pid":"dffd0eecd27b3cd87d1ca1cf376dee900a27e195","tid":1984574,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2498fceed784689867de29658f7c2576357cf975","tid":1984574,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14:03:37.000Z","msg":"超過十萬現金點樣可以洗底？ 買期油？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14:05:13.000Z","msg":"社署會要求支出單據，所以去澳門是不行的"},{"pid":"4c81b642e429a3ddd1400ed1be5486282d80a0db","tid":1984574,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2498fceed784689867de29658f7c2576357cf975","tid":1984574,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14:03:37.000Z","msg":"超過十萬現金點樣可以洗底？ 買期油？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14:05:23.000Z","msg":"負資產可以即上公屋"},{"pid":"2c0faa44de314e2956fbe72fd86de1947204712d","tid":1984574,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14:05:48.000Z","msg":"樓主申請咗未呀"},{"pid":"52525d4cda6cbddedc3a32e3b59359b3d6c6bd35","tid":1984574,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14:06:44.000Z","msg":"租d超豪華套房，好易用曬，又有單據"},{"pid":"98b6e1669445e4069dad7f2ace0bf855c292c338","tid":1984574,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4d5cb28101f9bd6f083bf7c90b127a53e8df796","tid":1984574,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14:04:31.000Z","msg":"一日洗五萬會唔會問你點解?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14:08:16.000Z","msg":"會"},{"pid":"007ae1267f700d4ea75ffb282465dd1c55bd0336","tid":1984574,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98b6e1669445e4069dad7f2ace0bf855c292c338","tid":1984574,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4d5cb28101f9bd6f083bf7c90b127a53e8df796","tid":1984574,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14:04:31.000Z","msg":"一日洗五萬會唔會問你點解?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14:08:16.000Z","msg":"會"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14:09:45.000Z","msg":"叫雞點拿單據?<br />\n打算享受一次明星雞破處就拿綜援"},{"pid":"e8e523b6013ed97292e4c61ed6b479f1be1ec88b","tid":1984574,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"007ae1267f700d4ea75ffb282465dd1c55bd0336","tid":1984574,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98b6e1669445e4069dad7f2ace0bf855c292c338","tid":1984574,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4d5cb28101f9bd6f083bf7c90b127a53e8df796","tid":1984574,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14:04:31.000Z","msg":"一日洗五萬會唔會問你點解?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14:08:16.000Z","msg":"會"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14:09:45.000Z","msg":"叫雞點拿單據?<br />\n打算享受一次明星雞破處就拿綜援"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14:10:54.000Z","msg":"佢當你收埋左d錢<br />\n<br />\nfail硬<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總之乜都要 invoice"},{"pid":"e80d0e937aee9a3ffe6ab43a9852720e39be1dcf","tid":1984574,"uid":301989,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14:13:44.000Z","msg":"直接講蝗話 話自己係支那國嚟 唔洗申請添 社處幫你搞晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"807f98cee8bdaa1e8de84e3b1eb94013b38c48e3","tid":1984574,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14:23:10.000Z","msg":"老貓果然係專業老綜"},{"pid":"47f65c2123e45a62452518a107c6bd10ea927351","tid":1984574,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14:27:38.000Z","msg":"申請方法及審批時間<br />\n<br />\n申請人可親自前往其區內的社會保障辦事處（須留意辦公時間會否受疫情影響）或用電話、傳真、電郵或郵遞方式提出申請，或由政府部門或其他非政府機構轉介。在接到申請後，社署職員會安排約見申請人<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>和進行家訪</strong></span>，以查核申請人的實際情況及所提供的資料。一般情況下，核實資料和審批手續可在4個星期內完成，但審批每個個案實際所需的時間，要視乎個別情況而定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://wealth.hket.com/article/2616896/%E3%80%90%E5%A4%B1%E6%A5%AD%E6%B4%A5%E8%B2%BC%E3%80%91%E5%A4%B1%E6%A5%AD%E9%99%A4%E4%BA%86%E5%8F%AF%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E7%B6%9C%E6%8F%B4%E5%A4%96%20%E9%82%84%E6%9C%89%E7%94%9A%E9%BA%BC%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E4%BF%9D%E9%9A%9C%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E6%8F%B4%E5%8A%A9%EF%BC%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwealth.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2616896%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E6%25B4%25A5%25E8%25B2%25BC%25E3%2580%2591%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E9%2599%25A4%25E4%25BA%2586%25E5%258F%25AF%25E7%2594%25B3%25E8%25AB%258B%25E7%25B6%259C%25E6%258F%25B4%25E5%25A4%2596%2520%25E9%2582%2584%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%2594%259A%25E9%25BA%25BC%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%259A%259C%25E6%258F%2590%25E4%25BE%259B%25E6%258F%25B4%25E5%258A%25A9%25EF%25BC%259F&d=uNNx3RetO4MSseDCYlD6CpnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=a530c307\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://wealth.hket.com/article/2616896/%E3%80%90%E5%A4%B1%E6%A5%AD%E6%B4%A5%E8%B2%BC%E3%80%91%E5%A4%B1%E6%A5%AD%E9%99%A4%E4%BA%86%E5%8F%AF%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E7%B6%9C%E6%8F%B4%E5%A4%96%20%E9%82%84%E6%9C%89%E7%94%9A%E9%BA%BC%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E4%BF%9D%E9%9A%9C%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E6%8F%B4%E5%8A%A9%EF%BC%9F</a>"},{"pid":"04da5fc9f8b43e6755ae48a3d540f75507f5a942","tid":1984574,"uid":92979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14:48:49.000Z","msg":"取消銀行戶口得唔得？"},{"pid":"81dbc42fe955774aa23a8d516260139e84dc4712","tid":1984574,"uid":328316,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14:51:58.000Z","msg":"香港新四大天王：《白卡，殘津，綜援，公屋》<br />\n<br />\n一個唔開心衝入急症話我想自殺！！！<br />\n恭喜獲得白卡一張<br />\n醫院班傻的嗎畜都冇咁得閒理你一個，求其話你痴線就打發你走<br />\n<br />\n之後扮自殺夠七次<br />\n儲齊七個青山醫院印花<br />\n貼落你張白卡度<br />\n同屋企人夾埋做戲扮不和吵大獲，繼而動武<br />\n證明你病情因為家庭關係惡劣所以惡化<br />\n就可以搵醫生社工幫你搞恩恤安置<br />\n獎品非常豐富，有機會獲得單人公屋一間<br />\nSUPER！！！！<br />\n<br />\n搵塊薯片割下脈，用意粉吊頸，撞下豆腐<br />\n得閒坐天台欄杆望下風景<br />\n就構成企圖自殺要上青山<br />\n誓要去 入青山！！！！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後一個唔高興，醫生評估你完全喪失工作能力<br />\n就有機會拎到傷殘津貼<br />\n<br />\n不過綜援+被評定為傷殘好似係最爽<br />\n經常需要護理=每個月食到政府$5850<br />\n<br />\n雖然得果六千都冇<br />\n不過香港有班人每個月得最低工資，例如賺得七千幾八千，之後要俾二三千屋企<br />\n你只不過係詐病呃下錢過日子，唔好要求咁高啦<br />\n<br />\n仲未計你有白卡，搭公共交通只需$2<br />\n新界西出港島藍色線好貴嫁<br />\n由$20一程變成$2一程，當你要每日來回，<br />\n本身成個月就食左你差唔多$900<br />\n之後就會由$900變$100以內<br />\n係咪好開心呢"},{"pid":"f8045ed078fa5f5701d0c39be96f69115cabe3bc","tid":1984574,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14:57:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你自己又唔攞？"},{"pid":"0865e1814d7628c1ac6f21dcaa622a56b397d218","tid":1984574,"uid":32219,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T15:00:02.000Z","msg":"有2隻貓 申唔申請得"},{"pid":"e34e42be329ab57555eccca9c76e78780824d51e","tid":1984574,"uid":128600,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T15:03:37.000Z","msg":"用緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89ea73da3efce0e501182c44be723b785949a693","tid":1984574,"uid":342527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T15:26:39.000Z","msg":"呃完都係幾千蚊 有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n俾啲大志啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3f06901ec8da1a540ecffe5cecd24ed14d05c34","tid":1984574,"uid":2590,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T15:43:31.000Z","msg":"研究如何攻破城市福利系統比到麥當勞工作更有價值。"},{"pid":"f11e7e5283e019517aff2a02c9c9fc532ddbaf8a","tid":1984574,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T03:32:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02c28941e1a982b167a356bdbae42e5e7af1f8e6","tid":1984574,"uid":65770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T10:46:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>超過十萬現金點樣可以洗底？ 買期油？</blockquote><del>負資產</del>白卡可以即上公屋</blockquote>"},{"pid":"d0956731ab338d808e1146c2d9c46b905007227c","tid":1984574,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T05:06:21.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"d3fbca08cb416c0a08fa489f52d3c864795f3c09","tid":1984574,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T05:11:20.000Z","msg":"提示 樓主日日叫人申請 自己日日返工"}]}